In Extract.cs, refactor `ComputeNested` by extracting the squaring pattern into a reusable method. Create a `Square` method and update the computation to use it.

New Square method:
// Postcondition: result >= 0
private int Square(int n)
{
    return n * n;
}

Updated ComputeNested using Square:
public int ComputeNested(int x, int y, int z)
{
    return Square(x) + Square(y) + Square(z);
}
